"      Hamill RJ, Robinson LM, Wexler HR, et al, &ldquo;Efficacy and Safety of Potassium Infusion Therapy in Hypokalemic Critically Ill Patients,&rdquo;",
"      <i>",
"       Crit Care Med",
"      </i>",
"      , 1991, 19(5):694-9.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
