"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?30/56/31626?source=related_link\">",
"      Unipolar depression in adults and selective serotonin reuptake inhibitors (SSRIs): Pharmacology, administration, and side effects",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?35/20/36169?source=related_link\">",
"      Unipolar depression in adults and tricyclic and tetracyclic drugs: Pharmacology, administration, and side effects",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?9/39/9850?source=related_link\">",
"      Unipolar depression in adults: Continuation and maintenance treatment",
"     </a>",
